definitions.definition: To place in a basket or baskets.
To cross-collateralize the royalty advances for multiple works so that the creator is not paid until all of those works have achieved a certain level of success.

main_definition: ( transitive ) To place in a basket or baskets.
secondary_definitions: ( transitive , publishing ) To cross-collateralize the royalty advances for multiple works so that the creator is not paid until all of those works have achieved a certain level of success.
